verbose_text: As shown in XREF_FIG, DASH, comparing to baseline, significantly reduced SBP at week one (mean change from baseline -10.65 +/- 12.89 mmHg, CI : -19.81, -2.49, P = 0.023), with sustained effect at week two (-9.60 +/- 11.23 mmHg, CI : -16.70, -2.50, P = 0.039).
evidence: DASH, comparing to baseline, significantly reduced SBP
